docs.text: Getting Start For full documentation visit mkdocs.org install pip install mkdocs Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs gh-deploy - Deploy your documentation to GitHub Pages. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit.
